bstituted about 112 cups of swiss chard, and let me tell you, that was an EXCELLENT choice!  I might actually do this every time.  I also had to use pecans instead of walnuts no big deal and I used a combination of ricotta and mozzarella instead of muenster cheese.  The cheeses were a BIG success as well.  I feel like my substitutions didn039t change the recipe too much, so I feel confident in giving this a 5star rating.  I will definitely be making this again.REVMy fiance loved it, but it didnt really blow me out of the water...then again its tough thinking of good recipes for squash!');
