spaetzle.REVI''m Hungarian. I go back to my family''s homes in Hungary every year for 68 weeks! This is the way they make their spsetzle. PREFECT! So yummy! Thank you! It bought me back home. AlizkaREVI made this tonight to go with chicken paprikash.  The dumplings were wonderful!  It made enough for about 68 people, so i sauteed half of them in butter and salt, and topped those with the chicken and used the other half for chicken and dumplings.  These are the perfect chewy consistency, just like I was looking for.Thanks for sharing your recipe!');

